de.hshl.obj.wavefront.obj

Class VertexMultiIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hshl.obj.meta.Reflective.DataClass
      • de.hshl.obj.wavefront.obj.VertexMultiIndex

  • public final class VertexMultiIndex
extends Reflective.DataClass
    Stores three indices, one for the position, on for the texture coordinate, and one for the normal. Can be hashed and compared, and thus can be used as key of a map.
    Author:
    Johannes Vollmer
    See Also:
    getPositionIndex(), getNormalIndex(), getTextureCoordinateIndex()
